</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='style' href='#style'></a> style</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>Style the element using CSS.</p>
</span></p><p class='default'>
Default value: <p>height: 1px, background-color: var(â€“secondary-text-color)</p>
</p></dd></dl>
</div>
